<h2>Mobile Services in the Healing Arts or Veterinary Medicine</h2>
<p>To provide mobile services, you must receive authorization before beginning the mobile service operation. Provide the information outlined in <a title="25 TAC &#0167;289.226(i) " href="/radiation/laws-rules.aspx#289226">25 TAC &#0167;289.226(g) </a>or <a title="RC Form 226-8" href="/radiation/forms.aspx#2268">RC Form 226-8</a>.</p>

<hr/>
<h2>Healing Arts Screening</h2>
<p>To conduct a healing arts screening program, you must receive authorization <strong><em>before</em></strong> beginning the screening program. Provide the information outlined in <a title="25 TAC &#0167;289.226(g) and (h)" href="/radiation/laws-rules.aspx#289226">25 TAC &#0167;289.226(g) and (h)</a>.</p>

<hr/>
<h2>Osteoporosis Screening</h2>
<p>To conduct a osteoporosis screening program, you must receive authorization <strong><em>before</em></strong> beginning the screening program. Provide the information outlined in <a title="RC Form 226-7" href="/radiation/forms.aspx#22610">RC Form 226-10</a>.</p>
<p>For information on self-referred osteoporosis screening, please see the <a title="Special Requirements and Exemptions" href="/radiation/x-ray/special-requirements.aspx">Special Requirements and Exemptions</a> page.</p>

<hr/>
<h2>Coronary Heart Disease Screening</h2>
<p>To conduct a coronary heart disease screening program, you must receive authorization <strong><em>before</em></strong> beginning the screening program. Provide the information outlined in RC Form <a title="RC Form 226-7" href="/radiation/forms.aspx#2269">RC Form 226-9</a>.</p>

